{"tid":947240,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"第五座歐洲金靴！美斯超越C.朗成歷史No.1","createTime":"2018-12-19T06:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T10:50:15.000Z","uid":54373,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"45182d3058f5a0afe2a54264c4ca784868bbd5f0","tid":947240,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:36:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://rs3.sinahk.net/cap/66/2018/12/18/f/f02651586d3e5fb4f24df5834c36de81.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frs3.sinahk.net%2Fcap%2F66%2F2018%2F12%2F18%2Ff%2Ff02651586d3e5fb4f24df5834c36de81.jpg&h=c33a693a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n祝賀美斯<br />\n<br />\n　　香港時間12月18日，美斯領取了2017/18賽季歐洲金靴獎，這是他連續第二年獲得歐洲金靴，同時也是個人生涯第五次獲此殊榮。<br />\n<br />\n　　美斯領取獎盃後表示：「能夠在世界上最好的球隊效力，和最好的球員踢球，讓一切變得輕鬆。所有的榮譽都像蛋糕上的櫻桃一樣，只有在隊友的幫助下，這一切才變得可能。」<br />\n<br />\n　　美斯在上季聯賽共攻入了34球，力壓32球的沙拿和30球的簡尼，以入球係數分68分成功獲得2017/18賽季的歐洲金靴。<br />\n<br />\n　　在此之前，美斯曾在2009/10賽季（34球）， 2011/2012賽季（50球）， 2012/2013賽季（46球）、2016/2017賽季（37球）贏得歐洲金靴獎，此次獲獎，也意味著美斯成功超越了4度獲獎的C.朗拿度，成為歷史上獲得歐洲金靴最多的球員。<br />\n<br />\n　　近5年歐洲金靴獎得主：<br />\n　　2017-2018 美斯（巴塞，34球）<br />\n　　2016-2017 美斯（巴塞，37球）<br />\n　　2015-2016 蘇亞雷斯（巴塞，40球）<br />\n　　2014-2015 C.朗拿度（皇馬，48球）<br />\n　　2013-2014 蘇亞雷斯（利物浦，31球）/C.朗拿度（皇馬，31球）"},{"pid":"ef662199611eae3a26d98c35402d15540a597c91","tid":947240,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"48球果年真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a707db997cc41ab0b5bc0a000035779ca8024443","tid":947240,"uid":54373,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"ef662199611eae3a26d98c35402d15540a597c91","tid":947240,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"48球果年真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:47:03.000Z","msg":"91球個年呢?"},{"pid":"3f592e6bdbd436a82ddb195ebea8cd2a3e86b947","tid":947240,"uid":36716,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:51:36.000Z","msg":"能夠在世界上最好的球隊效力，和最好的球員踢球，讓一切變得輕鬆。所有的榮譽都像蛋糕上的櫻桃一樣，只有在隊友的幫助下，這一切才變得可能。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對比<br />\n<br />\n我就是歷史最佳球員"},{"pid":"922bd3becb6b6343bb6a170944701b815225a927","tid":947240,"uid":38172,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:57:01.000Z","msg":"美斯領取獎盃後表示：「能夠在世界上最好的球隊效力，和最好的球員踢球，讓一切變得輕鬆。所有的榮譽都像蛋糕上的櫻桃一樣，只有在隊友的幫助下，這一切才變得可能。」<br />\n<br />\n美斯D中文幾好, 又識用比喻<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75609d8ce700b0a854e77a0dd13283ec52b9111b","tid":947240,"uid":90515,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"ef662199611eae3a26d98c35402d15540a597c91","tid":947240,"uid":5549,"like":2,"dislike":8,"score":-6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T06:42:02.000Z","msg":"48球果年真係好痴線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T07:15:20.000Z","msg":"12年好似50球"},{"pid":"ed6514060ceec66ce6a8d1c4b8cddaf047101413","tid":947240,"uid":68375,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:51:44.000Z","msg":"有咩咁出奇，唔想再討論美斯了"},{"pid":"be23af314c634dde29a7e6b48d651ead1359f10c","tid":947240,"uid":29993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:53:43.000Z","msg":"牙蘇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b200eec04472dcbadec592bed69c99be81604fc3","tid":947240,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"坐左一年監，想問下今年金球獎得主魔笛入左幾多球？"},{"pid":"74f00304390f61ce68ac589ee1e3c851dfb3147f","tid":947240,"uid":1560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b200eec04472dcbadec592bed69c99be81604fc3","tid":947240,"uid":21398,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T09:55:14.000Z","msg":"坐左一年監，想問下今年金球獎得主魔笛入左幾多球？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T10:15:43.000Z","msg":"有冇聽過豆住中